" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers\u003C/change>\n\t\t\u003Cchange when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography\u003C/change>\n\t    \u003Cchange when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#JP\">Updated Zenodo DOI\u003C/change>\n            \t\u003Cchange when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2023-05-04\" who=\"#SS\">added milestones to indicate change of face; line numbers run sequentially\u003C/change>\n\t\u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000784_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000784.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Cmilestone unit=\"face\" n=\"a\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>D\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>is\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>M\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>anibus\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>s\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>acrum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>Vibia · Arete vix\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">it\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\">annis\u003C/supplied>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cnum value=\"30\">XXX\u003C/num>\n                    \u003Cmilestone unit=\"face\" n=\"b\"/>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>Vibius · \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Aptitian\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>us\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> pi\u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">ae\u003C/supplied> \u003Csupplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>fec\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>it\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/supplied>    \n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Korhonen 2004\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#AA\">\n                \u003Cp>Sacred to the spirits of the underworld. Vibia Arete lived for 30 years; Vibius Aptitianus built this\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--DM[S] header; of Vibia Arete, age in years (30); ?erected by? Vibius Aptitianus (name attested also at Catania, CIL X.7062; although Mommsen sought to amend): Dis Manibus Vibia Arete vixit annis XXX. And on the rim of the plaque, Vibius Aptitianus Pi- - -. As Manganaro observes, Libertini offers an inaccurate reading, which AE in turn reproduces. One of several plaques in Catania museum on which a pair of feet are depicted! Signif. disputed, but perhaps augural?-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1984.0442\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IMusCatania\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Korhonen\u003C/author>\n                         \u003Cdate>2004\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>143\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/2EUC82DH\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Libertini\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1931\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>49 no.5-6 = Libertini (1981) 99 no.5-6\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/T67M4XMU\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001870\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Manganaro\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1961\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>183 no.1 ph\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/HXK7DASC\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001852\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001852\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
